Q: What qualities will you and the board be looking for in Enron's next CEO?=
=20
A: We'll be looking for a good, strong leader, a very effective leader [who]=
 really knows our business -- all our businesses, not just what they're runn=
ing today. We're also looking for a good people person who is able to motiva=
te others and get strong performances out of people. We need someone who is =
